{
  "name": "listing-doctor-mcp",
  "version": "1.0.0",
  "description": "MCP server for Etsy listing optimization — score titles, tags, descriptions, photos & conversion on a 100-point scale. AI-powered SEO analysis with letter grades (A–F) and prioritized fix recommendations. Works with Claude, Cursor, Windsurf, and any MCP-compatible AI client.",
